            "annotations": {
              "comment": "Clear delineation between the scope of a problem versus a diagnosis is\n                                not easy to achieve in practice. For the purposes of clinical documentation with this\n                                archetype, problem and diagnosis are regarded as a continuum, with increasing levels of\n                                detail and supportive evidence usually providing weight towards the label of\n                                'diagnosis'.\n                            "
